org.microbean.configuration.cdi.annotation

Annotation Type Configured


  • @Documented
 @Qualifier
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value={FIELD,METHOD,PARAMETER,TYPE})
public @interface Configured
    A Qualifier designating something that has been configured.

    This annotation is reserved for future use.

    Laird Nelson
